Xc_compound
--- Alpha 1

This is a remake of the original cs_compound map made by Valve in climb style.
This map is still in alpha version, so there will be a lot of bugs found in.
Anyway the map was designed to climb without checkpoints. If you make use of them, be sure that some functions don't work properly anymore!

When you find a bug, report it to me, I'll fix it in the next version, if I make one.

Have Fun & Good Luck
--- www.illpillow.de
